'''加文·普雷托尔-平尼'''（{{lang-en|Gavin Edmund Pretor-Pinney}}，{{bd|1950年|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[大众科学|科普]]作家<ref name="csguide">{{cite web|url=http://www.convilleandwalsh.com/index.php/authors/author/gavin-pretor-pinney/|title=The Cloudspotter's Guide|publisher=[[Conville_and_Walsh|Conville and Walsh]]|accessdate=2020-11-20|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005164810/http://www.convilleandwalsh.com/index.php/authors/author/gavin-pretor-pinney/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，毕业于[[西敏公學|西敏公學]]和[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]，主要作品有《云彩收集者手册》（''The Cloud Collector's Handbook''，2006）、《{{le|波行天下|The Wavewatcher's Companion}}：从神经脉冲到登月计划》（''The Wavewatcher's Companion''，2010）等<ref name="wwcomp">{{cite web |url=http://cloudappreciationsociety.org/wavewatchers-companion/ |title=The Wavewatcher’s Companion |accessdate=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2016-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910021721/https://cloudappreciationsociety.org/wavewatchers-companion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/7814714/The-Wavewatchers-Companion-by-Gavin-Pretor-Pinney-review.html |title=Daily Telegraph review |location=London |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=13 June 2010 |accessdate=2020-11-20 |archive-date=2017-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515190749/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/7814714/The-Wavewatchers-Companion-by-Gavin-Pretor-Pinney-review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

